<template>
  <div class="orderConfirm">
    <van-pull-refresh
      v-model="isLoading"
      @refresh="handleRefreshPage"
      success-text="刷新成功"
    >
      <!-- 头部支付信息 -->
      <!-- <div class="hand_status">
        <div class="head_title" v-if="orderMess.status == 0">支付未完成</div>
        <div class="head_title" v-else>支付已完成</div>
        <div class="head_price">订单总价：￥{{ orderMess.totalprice }}</div>
      </div> -->
      <!-- 个人信息 -->
      <van-cell-group class="message_box">
        <van-cell title="订单总价：" :value="orderMess.totalprice" />
        <van-cell title="体检单位：" :value="orderMess.companyname" />
        <van-cell
          title="姓名证件："
          :value="`${orderMess.name}(${orderMess.idcard})`"
        />
        <van-cell title="手机号码：" :value="orderMess.telephone" />
        <van-cell title="体检日期：" :value="orderMess.checkdate" />
        <van-cell title="体检地址：" :value="orderMess.address" />
        <!-- 源-体检须知： -->
        <van-cell title="注意事项：">
          <template #default>
            <div
              class="link_look"
              @click="handleShowDialog(textContent, '注意事项')"
            >
              点击查看
            </div>
          </template>
        </van-cell>
        <!-- <van-cell title="注意事项：">
          <template #default>
            <div
              class="link_look"
              @click="handleShowDialog(orderMess.setmealremind, '注意事项')"
            >
              点击查看
            </div>
          </template>
        </van-cell> -->
        <van-cell title="下单时间：" :value="orderMess.operatdate" />
        <van-cell title="订单编号：">
          <template #default>
            <div class="code">{{ orderMess.regid }}</div>
            <van-image
              class="link_img"
              :src="`data:image/png;base64,${orderMess.barcode}`"
            />
          </template>
        </van-cell>
      </van-cell-group>
      <!-- 套餐信息 -->
      <div class="project_box">
        <!-- 套餐外项目 -->
        <div class="combine_box">
          <div class="title">套餐外项目（{{ combineitems.length }}）</div>
          <van-cell-group>
            <van-cell
              v-for="item in combineitems"
              :key="item.combinecode"
              :value="item.combinename"
            />
          </van-cell-group>
        </div>
        <!-- 套餐内项目 -->
        <div class="setmeal_box">
          <div class="title">套餐内项目（{{ setmealitems.length }}）</div>
          <van-cell-group>
            <van-cell
              v-for="item in setmealitems"
              :key="item.combinecode"
              :value="item.combinename"
            />
          </van-cell-group>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 底部按钮信息 -->
    </van-pull-refresh>
    <div class="footer">
      <van-button
        v-for="item in operateitems"
        :key="item.code"
        type="info"
        size="small"
        @click="handleClickOperate(item)"
        >{{ item.name }}</van-button
      >
      <!-- <van-button type="info" size="small">继续支付</van-button>
      <van-button type="info" size="small">取消预约</van-button> -->
    </div>
    <van-dialog
      class="setmealwarnmsg_dia"
      v-model="showDialog"
      messageAlign
      :title="showDialogTitle"
    >
      <div class="setmealwarnmsg">
        <div class="warnmsg_content" v-html="dialogContent"></div>
      </div>
    </van-dialog>
  </div>
</template>
<script>
import {
  getListData,
  healthCheckForH5Post,
  cancelAppoint,
} from "@/api/reservation.js";
export default {
  name: "",

  components: {},

  data() {
    return {
      orderid: "",
      isLoading: false,
      orderUrl: require("@/assets/images/order.jpg"),
      orderMess: {},
      setmealitems: [],
      combineitems: [],
      operateitems: [],
      showDialog: false, // 体检须知 // 注意事项
      dialogContent: "",
      showDialogTitle: "",
      textContent: `<h2 style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; text-align: center;font-size:0.4rem;font-weight: 600;">健康体检注意事项</h2>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">体检要求:</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;您好，欢迎您来体检!体检前请您仔细阅读体检注意事项:</p>
<h4 style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="color: #3598db;font-size:0.38rem;font-weight: 600;"><strong>一、体检前:</strong></span></h4>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（1）于体检前一天晚餐后，不再进食，以保证空腹8-10小时抽血检验。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（2）体检前2～3日以清淡饮食为主，不吃高脂性及油炸性食物，禁食血制品及含铁量过高的食物（如猪血、鸡血、海带、菠菜等），避免剧烈运动，不饮酒或尽量少饮酒。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（3）糖尿病、高血压、心脏病、哮喘等慢性病患者，请将平日服用的药物携带备用，受检日建议不要停药，可以在抽血前用少量白开水服用药物。14碳呼气试验1个月内不能服用消炎药。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（4）受检者不宜化妆，检查时避免穿连衣裙、连裤袜等，不要佩戴金属饰物或携带贵重物品，以防丢失或影响检查。</p>
<h4 style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="color: #3598db;font-size:0.38rem;font-weight: 600;">二、体检中:</span></h4>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（1）抽血检查：</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;需空腹8&mdash;10小时。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（2）X光检查：</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ① 女士请勿穿连衣裙，并取下文胸及有字母扣的衣服和项链、玉佩等饰品。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ② 备孕者（男、女）和孕妇，应事先告知医护人员，勿做X光检查。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（3）心电图检查：</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;女士请勿穿连衣裙、连体袜，检查时需解开文胸。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（4）彩超检查：</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;① 腹部彩超需空腹（需空腹，可喝水） 。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;② 子宫附件彩超需膀胱充盈（憋尿），阴道彩超仅限已婚或有性生活史女性检查。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;③ 泌尿系彩超需膀胱充盈（憋尿） 。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（5）尿常规检查：</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;① 建议留取中段尿（女性月经期不宜留尿检查，待经期结束3-5天后再补检）。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;② 留尿前请到体检前台领取留尿管及尿杯，留尿时需留取2/3管并拧紧盖子，尿液标本放在卫生间门口标本架内。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（6）妇科检查： （仅限已婚或有性生活史女性）</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;① 需排空小便，月经期不宜妇科检查，月经干净后3&mdash;5天检查。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;② 若同选阴道彩超和妇科检查者，应先检查妇科项目后再检查阴道彩超。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;③ 检查前一天禁止阴道用药，禁止同房。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（7）血压检查：</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;应静坐10分钟以上，以免误差。</p>
<h4 style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';"><span style="color: #3598db;font-size:0.38rem;font-weight: 600;">三、体检后:</span></h4>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（1）全部项目检查完毕后请把导检单交回收单处，以便我们尽快整理和汇总体检报告。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">（2）请在单位结账之前完成体检，谢谢您的配合。</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';">&nbsp;</p>`,
      // <p style="font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei'; text-align: right;">惠州市第六人民医院健康管理中心</p>
    };
  },

  mounted() {
    this.orderid = this.$route.query.orderid || "";
    if (!this.orderid) {
      this.$toast.success("获取订单编码!");
      return;
    }
    this.handleGetListData(); // 获取订单详情接口返回
  },

  methods: {
    handleRefreshPage() {
      this.isLoading = true;
      this.handleGetListData(); // 获取订单详情接口返回
    },
    // 取消预约接口
    handleCancelAppoint() {
      cancelAppoint([
        `${this.orderMess.regid}-${localStorage.getItem("customercode")}`,
      ]).then((res) => {
        if (res.data.result) {
          this.$toast.success(res.data.message);
          this.$router.push({
            path: "/orderListPage",
          });
          // this.handleGetListData(); // 获取订单详情接口返回
        }
      });
    },
    // 支付页面接口
    handlePayInfo() {
      healthCheckForH5Post({
        businesstype: "PayInfo",
        code: this.orderid,
      }).then((res) => {
        if (!res.data.result) return;
        if (res.data.result.payUrl) {
          window.open(res.data.result.payUrl);
        } else {
          this.$toast.success(res.data.message);
          this.$router.push({ path: "/orderListPage" });
        }
      });
    },
    // 查看报告页面
    handleCustomerReportDetail() {
      this.$router.push({
        path: "/orderMessage",
        query: { obj: this.orderMess.regid },
      });
    },
    // 点击操作按钮回调
    handleClickOperate(item) {
      console.log(item);
      if (!item) return;
      switch (item.code) {
        case "PayInfo": // 支付页面
          this.handlePayInfo();
          break;
        case "CancelAppoint": // 取消预约
          this.handleCancelAppoint();
          break;
        case "CustomerReportDetail": // 查看报告
          this.handleCustomerReportDetail();
          break;
        default:
          break;
      }
    },
    // 点击弹框回调
    handleShowDialog(content, title) {
      this.dialogContent = content;
      this.showDialogTitle = title;
      this.showDialog = true;
    },
    // 获取订单详情接口返回
    handleGetListData() {
      getListData({
        businesstype: "OrderDetail",
        code: this.orderid,
        customercode: localStorage.getItem("customercode"),
      })
        .then((res) => {
          this.$toast.success("加载完成");
          this.isLoading = false;
          this.orderMess = res.data.result;
          this.operateitems = res.data.result.operateitems;
          this.setmealitems = res.data.result.combineitems.filter((k) => {
            return k.addflag == 0;
          });
          this.combineitems = res.data.result.combineitems.filter((k) => {
            return k.addflag != 0;
          });
        })
        .catch((err) => {
          this.isLoading = false;
        });
    },
  },

  watch: {},

  computed: {},
};
</script>
<style lang='scss' scoped>
.orderConfirm {
  height: calc(100vh - 94px);
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  padding: 5px;
  position: relative;

  .van-pull-refresh::-webkit-scrollbar {
    display: none;
  }
  .van-pull-refresh {
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 8px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    .hand_status {
      height: 60px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
      .head_title {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #e6a23c;
      }
      .head_price {
        margin-top: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
    .message_box {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
    }
    .project_box {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding-bottom: 60px;
      .combine_box {
        .title {
          height: 38px;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          font-size: 16px;
          font-weight: 600;
          color: #000;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
          box-sizing: border-box;
          padding-left: 10px;
          position: relative;
        }
        .title::before {
          content: "";
          width: 5px;
          height: 50%;
          border-radius: 5px;
          background-color: #e6a23c;
          position: absolute;
          left: 0;
        }
      }
      .setmeal_box {
        .title {
          height: 38px;
          display: flex;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          font-size: 16px;
          font-weight: 600;
          color: #000;
          border-bottom: 1px solid #d8d8d8;
          box-sizing: border-box;
          position: relative;
          padding-left: 10px;
        }
        .title::before {
          content: "";
          width: 5px;
          height: 50%;
          border-radius: 5px;
          background-color: #e6a23c;
          position: absolute;
          left: 0;
        }
      }
    }
  }
  .footer {
    width: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    height: 45px;
    background-color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    .van-button {
      width: 80px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
  }
  .setmealwarnmsg_dia {
    width: 320px;
    .setmealwarnmsg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      padding: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      overflow: auto;
      .warnmsg_content {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        word-wrap: break-word;
      }
    }
  }
}
</style>
<style lang="scss">
.orderConfirm {
  .message_box {
    .van-cell {
      padding: 8px;
      .van-cell__title {
        flex: unset;
        width: 28% !important;
      }
      .van-cell__value {
        flex: unset;
        width: 71% !important;
        text-align: left;
        .link_look {
          color: #e6a23c;
        }
        .link_img {
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
</style>